	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="indent(1)">To</p>
				<p>the <addressee>Reverend Is. Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">minister of the Jewish Congregation</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">at</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi></placeName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>The Hague</placeName> <date>20 <hi rend="underline">August</hi> 54</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Reverend Sir&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Two years since I have had the honor<lb/> to receive direct tidings from you and I did<lb/> not neglect in transmitting to you some publi&#45;<lb/>cations of a nature to Interest you.  As I did<lb/> not hear the good receipt of those works&#44; I<lb/> avail me of a favorable occasion to inform<lb/> me of your health and to assure you of my<lb/> good wishes for your continuation of the beau&#45;<lb/>tiful task to excite the religious feelings of<lb/> our coreligionists in the new world.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">If&#44; by occasion&#44; you could transmit<lb/> me some numbers of the <hi rend="underline">Occident</hi>&#44; and principally<lb/> those wherein papers of your hand and that<lb/> of your lamented friend <persName>M. de Silva Solis</persName>&#8212;a<lb/> relation of me&#8212;have appeared&#44; you will furnish<lb/> me a new proof of your kindness and aim<lb/> to guide my views on the Jewish interests in<lb/> the <placeName>West</placeName>.</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I have taken the liberty to deliver a<lb/> letter for <sic>recommandation</sic> to your benevolence<lb/> to <persName>Mr. B. d&#39;Ancona</persName>&#44; now living at your town and<lb/> who has sailed for <placeName>America</placeName> a year ago.<lb/>  He is well arrived&#59; if you could <sic>given</sic> me<lb/> some information on his account&#44; you will<lb/> do my great pleasure.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">You may be assured&#44; reverend Sir&#44;<lb/> I will be very happy to prove to you&#44;<lb/> in my country&#44; I am very truly your humble</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Servant</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">T J Belinfante</persName></p>
		</body>
